lead_paragraph: In-form Victoria Azarenka battled past an ailing but determined second seed Angelique Kerber to set up a Miami Open final showdown against Svetlana Kuznetsova with a 6-2 7-5 victory on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Azarenka Avenges Kerber Loss to Reach Miami Final
